Cameron Bender https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cameron_Bender 0 Cameron Frederick Bender (born November 20, 1974) is an American actor. He is known for playing the role of Chilton Chivers in Goodnight Burbank and Richard in Mistresses. He also appeared on the sitcom Rules of Engagement as Rick.
